---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Servicios"
  descripcion="Servicios profesionales de Cloud Operations, DevOps, Kubernetes, Terraform y CI/CD con más de 4 años de experiencia real."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <p class="text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Servicios</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-6 max-w-2xl">
      Soluciones cloud con experiencia real en producción
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-xl">
      Cada servicio está respaldado por años de trabajo en entornos reales — no demos, no tutoriales.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- AWS -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h10a4 4 0 001-7.9A5 5 0 106 6.6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">AWS Cloud Infrastructure</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Diseño y gestión de infraestructuras multi-AZ altamente disponibles y tolerantes a fallos en AWS. Desde arquitecturas simples hasta entornos complejos con múltiples cuentas y zonas de disponibilidad.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>VPC, subnets públicas y privadas, NAT Gateways</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>EC2, ECS, EKS — según el caso de uso</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>RDS, S3, CloudFront, Route 53</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>IAM, Security Groups, políticas de acceso mínimo</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>CloudWatch, alertas y dashboards de monitoreo</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["EC2","ECS","EKS","ECR","RDS","S3","CloudFront","Route53","CloudWatch","VPC","IAM","EBS","EFS","Glacier"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IaC -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Infrastructure as Code</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Infraestructura reproducible, versionada y auditada. Entornos DEV, TEST y PROD consistentes desde el primer día, sin configuración manual y sin sorpresas.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Módulos Terraform reutilizables y versionados</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Gestión de estado remoto con S3 + DynamoDB</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Ansible para gestión de configuración y parches</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Entornos DEV/TEST/PROD desde variables</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Revisión de cambios antes de aplicar (plan)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Terraform","Ansible","Git","GitHub","S3 Backend","DynamoDB Lock","tfvars","Workspaces"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CI/CD -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">CI/CD Pipelines</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Pipelines completamente automatizados con calidad de código integrada en cada despliegue. Desde el commit hasta producción sin intervención manual.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Integración con GitHub Actions y Jenkins</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Build, test, análisis de calidad y deploy automático</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>SonarQube para análisis estático de código</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>ArgoCD para GitOps en Kubernetes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Nexus como repositorio de artefactos</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Jenkins","GitHub Actions","ArgoCD","Maven","SonarQube","Nexus","Docker","ECR"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Kubernetes -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Kubernetes & Contenedores</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Orquestación de contenedores en producción con despliegues GitOps, gestión con Helm y administración visual con Lens.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Clusters EKS en AWS con nodos administrados</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Helm Charts para despliegues reproducibles</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>GitOps con ArgoCD — código como fuente de verdad</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Docker multi-stage para imágenes optimizadas</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>ECR como registro privado de imágenes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Kubernetes","Docker","Helm","EKS","ECR","ArgoCD","Lens","Docker Compose"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Monitoreo -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Observabilidad & Monitoreo</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Visibilidad total de la infraestructura con alertas proactivas y dashboards en tiempo real. Detecta problemas antes de que afecten a los usuarios.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Prometheus para recolección de métricas</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Grafana para dashboards personalizados</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>CloudWatch para logs y alertas en AWS</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Alertas proactivas por email y Slack</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Gestión de incidencias con Jira</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Prometheus","Grafana","CloudWatch","Jira","HAProxy","DNS","TCP/IP"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Linux -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Linux & Automatización</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">Administración de servidores Linux y automatización de tareas repetitivas con scripting. Menos trabajo manual, más tiempo para lo que importa.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Administración de CentOS, Ubuntu y Red Hat</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Scripts Bash para automatización de tareas</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Gestión de volúmenes con LVM</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>VMware para virtualización on-premise</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-teal-400"></span>Python para scripts de automatización avanzados</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Tecnologías</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Ubuntu","CentOS","Red Hat","Debian","Alpine","Bash","Python","VMware","LVM"].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">¿Tienes un proyecto en mente?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto">Cuéntame qué estás construyendo y te ayudo a llevarlo a producción con las mejores prácticas.</p>
      <a href="/contacto" class="bg-teal-600 text-white text-sm font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors">
        Contactar
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
